resources.string: Serivise zoroshye zirashoboka ariko ntizikora, urashobora kugerageza kongera gukora cyangwa gutangira terefone yawe
Kunanirwa gushoboza serivisi igerwaho nuburenganzira bwumuzi
Koresha serivise ibanza kugirango porogaramu yawe ikore
Ibikorwa bya serivisi byoroshye bigomba gushobozwa gukora (byabitswe)
Ugomba gufungura idirishya rireremba kugirango urebe igiti (ikintu cyabitswe)
Nyuma yo gufungura, gukoresha inyandiko bizahita bifungura serivisi igerwaho nuburenganzira bwimizi (ikintu cyabitswe)
Mu buryo bwikora bushoboza serivisi zifite uburenganzira bwumuzi
Isesengura ryimiterere irahamye iyo ishoboye, ariko umubare muto wimyandikire ntishobora gukora neza. Ongera utangire serivisi igerwaho kugirango itangire gukurikizwa
Koresha inyandiko nyuma yo gufungura porogaramu
Imigaragarire ya logi ntabwo igaragara, kandi inkunga yinyandiko irasabwa gufungura iyi interface ubutaha
Porogaramu ikeneye gufungura \"Serivise %s \" kugirango ikore, nyamuneka fungura \"Igenamiterere-> Serivisi zoroshye\" cyangwa \"Igenamiterere-> Serivisi zoroshye-
Umurongo wo kumenyesha uzahora werekana \"Iyi porogaramu ikora\" imenyesha kugirango porogaramu ikomeze
Irasaba uruhushya rwo gufungura intera inyuma
Irasaba uruhushya rwo gufungura interineti inyuma kugirango ikore, nyamuneka jya kumiterere kugirango ufungure
Nyamuneka shoboza uruhushya mbere yo gukora!
